{"tid":1302580,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌","createTime":"2019-07-10T03:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T04:52:01.000Z","uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d7312821eed6619e12e87cbbc6e4a695a3a925","tid":1302580,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人)<br />\n<br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，?務局聯繫。 <br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。 <br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司權力核心。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我迫不及待好想玩玩了。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"14e6e49a69ec8bf3898f9474f07d617b4a86eac7","tid":1302580,"uid":136625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"又呢篇 悶路悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96946f94711cf7f74598481567717e72b1235cc","tid":1302580,"uid":164442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上水遊行路線更新</strong></span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302535</a><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c3ffad251fcca5aca631c1fbf89e6df6fae878","tid":1302580,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14e6e49a69ec8bf3898f9474f07d617b4a86eac7","tid":1302580,"uid":136625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"又呢篇 悶路悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:59:41.000Z","msg":"大學應該能考上，但心儀科系則不行了。繼續讀上還是不讀好？ <br />\n思索了半個月，還沒結果，待審核。 <br />\n科系會和你日後的工作有關，跟足一輩子，加上沒興趣很難考得好，可以連畢業也會成問題。 <br />\n還是再给自己多一年機會？再拼一拼？"},{"pid":"0543e83e8fcac1665451a3ceb3e360ee0557716e","tid":1302580,"uid":124891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"跑完10000米了～<br />\n今天天氣好好，但好累。<br />\n有微風"},{"pid":"38b259fcffe3061d97d2a53068b630b90c30540c","tid":1302580,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"無論你哪裡畢業，出來工作也要由低做起。 <br />\n所以 Thei 和港大，沒有分別。degree，一樣。之不過一個是大學生活，另一個是學院生活。"},{"pid":"dc573a31acfbf7486b162a6ba4a3cb13e31924cf","tid":1302580,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fde070bec2134892f97ee145f7d9c16ec23a9de","tid":1302580,"uid":32861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a887013e1b50663894809be2bfa05d2c1e976a","tid":1302580,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"見到其他人已經打算 讀HD/副學士，到台灣/內地 升學 ；而我&hellip;&hellip; 重考一年。&nbsp;<br />\n感覺極糟，原地踏步。&nbsp;<br />\n不過，我的目標由此至终也沒變；&nbsp;<br />\n香港公開大學 檢測及認證 ，收19~20分&nbsp;<br />\n不後侮，繼續走我的路。要努力，堅強，邁向未來，今年畢竟只是失手，考試太急躁了。"}]}